{{ja-noun|かげ}}

# [[shadow]]
#: {{ja-usex|馬の'''影'''|うま の '''かげ'''|a '''shadow''' of a horse}}
# a [[shape]] or form [[reflected]] in [[light]]
# [[presence]]
#: {{ja-usex|この町は'''影'''が薄い。|この まち は '''かげ''' が うすい。|This town's '''presence''' is little.}}
# [[negative]] [[aspect]]

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|影%法師|かげ%ぼうし}}: [[silhouette]], [[shadow]]
* {{ja-r|月影|つきかげ}}
* {{ja-r|空影|そらかげ}}
* {{ja-r|山影|やまかげ}}
* {{ja-r|闇影|やみかげ}}
* {{ja-r|日%影|ひ%かげ}}
{{der-bottom}}

{{ja-kanjitab|えい|yomi=kanon}}
From {{der|ja|ltc|sort=えい|-}} {{ltc-l|影}}.

The ''[[漢音#Japanese|kan'on]]'' pronunciation, so likely a later borrowing.

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|暗影|あんえい}}: [[shadow]], [[gloom]]
* {{ja-r|黒影|こくえい}}: [[silhouette]], [[dark]] shadow
* {{ja-r|人影|じんえい}}: [[figure]]/[[shadow]] of a [[person]]
{{der-bottom}}

{{ja-kanjitab|よう|yomi=goon}}
From {{der|ja|ltc|sort=よう|-}} {{ltc-l|影}}.

The ''[[呉音#Japanese|goon]]'' pronunciation, so likely the initial borrowing.

